divs: sighting detailson 2\11\13 i was going downtown to an appointment and went to a trax stn to catch train,while waiting i took 5 pics of my reflection in a glass panel,hours later at home i looked at the pics i took and in the 4th pic is an alien looking creature bout 18" tall,big head,big black eyes,4 arms,staring at me on my side of the glass! i've filed a discloser but i'm having trouble finding the right people,i emailed nick pope and he have me this site,i called and was told to file this report,so i look forward to hearing from someone soon! this is an amazing pic and you don't want to not see it!!!!
Summary: I didn't see UFO,took a pic and when I got home later found an alien like creature in one of the pics
